msgid "13000:[name]拓巳[line]「い、いや、違うよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "13000:[name]拓巳[line]N-No...[%p]"

msgid "13100:[name]拓巳[line]「見返りなんて、ひ、必要ないって、こと……。普通に、か、貸すよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "13100:[name]拓巳[line]I-I just mean... I don't need anything in return. I'll let you borrow it for free.[%p]"

msgid "13200:[name]梨深[line]「タク……」[%p]"
msgstr "13200:[name]梨深[line]Taku...[%p]"

msgid "13300:[name]梨深[line]「ありがとうっ」[%p]"
msgstr "13300:[name]梨深[line]Thank you.[%p]"

msgid "13400:満面の笑み。[linebreak]すごく嬉しそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "13400:She gave me a brilliant smile. She looked so happy.[%p]"

msgid "13500:僕に抱きついてきそうな勢い。[%p]"
msgstr "13500:I thought she might jump on me and give me a hug right there.[%p]"

msgid "13600:普段、女の子に喜ばれることなんて滅多にないから、僕まで嬉しくなる。[%p]"
msgstr "13600:Normally, girls were never happy about anything I did, so it made me happy, too.[%p]"

msgid "13700:ゆ、勇気を出して言ってみて、よかった……。[%p]"
msgstr "13700:I-I was glad I worked up the courage to say she could borrow it.[%p]"

msgid "13800:[name]梨深[line]「ビシィ！\u3000じゃあ見返りなしで借ります！」[%p]"
msgstr "13800:[name]梨深[line]Snap! Okay, I'll borrow it without giving you anything in return![%p]"

msgid "13900:[name]梨深[line]「となれば、善は急げ。タクの家にレッツゴー♪」[%p]"
msgstr "13900:[name]梨深[line]Let's get going, then! Let's head to your house![%p]"

msgid "14000:なんとか無事にベースまで戻ってこられた。[%p]"
msgstr "14000:I managed to get back to the Base safely.[%p]"

msgid "14100:もちろん梨深のおかげだ。感謝してる。[%p]"
msgstr "14100:Of course, it was thanks to Rimi. I was grateful to her.[%p]"

msgid "14200:ただ、部屋の中を片付けるからちょっと待っててほしいっていう[linebreak]僕の頼みをあっさり却下したのは、どうかと思う。[%p]"
msgstr "14200:I wished she hadn't refused me when I asked for a little time to clean up my room before she came in, though.[%p]"

msgid "14300:[name]梨深[line]「だって、前に来たときに汚いっていうのはよーく分かったし。今さら片付けたって無駄だよ」[%p]"
msgstr "14300:[name]梨深[line]I know exactly how dirty it is from the last time I was here. There's no point in trying to clean it up now.[%p]"

msgid "14400:[name]梨深[line]「かっこつけなくてもいいって。あたしとタクの仲でしょ。ね♪」[%p]"
msgstr "14400:[name]梨深[line]You don't need to try and hide anything from me. You and I are too close for that. Right? ♪[%p]"

msgid "14500:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "14500:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "14600:どんな仲なんだ……。[%p]"
msgstr "14600:Were we too close for that?[%p]"

msgid "14700:僕の記憶からは梨深のことはすっぽりと抜け落ちている。[linebreak]だから、よく分からない。[%p]"
msgstr "14700:My memories of Rimi were completely gone. So... I didn't really know.[%p]"

msgid "14800:たまに、梨深の馴れ馴れしさに驚かされる。"
msgstr "14800:Sometimes I was surprised at how overly-friendly Rimi seemed."

msgid "14900:[linebreak]それは決して不快ってわけじゃないけど、僕と梨深とで距離感に齟齬が生まれているのは確かだ。[%p]"
msgstr "14900:[linebreak]It didn't really bother me, but it was clear that there was a difference in how we felt about personal space.[%p]"

msgid "15000:たまに、梨深の馴れ馴れしさに驚かされる。それは決して不快ってわけじゃないけど、僕と梨深とで距離感に齟齬が生まれているのは確かだ。"
msgstr "15000:Sometimes I was surprised at how overly-friendly Rimi seemed. It didn't really bother me, but it was clear that there was a difference in how we felt about personal space."

msgid "15100:そもそも部屋を片付けなくても平気だなんて、梨深は本気で言ってるんだろうか。[%p]"
msgstr "15100:Was she really serious when she said she didn't care if I cleaned up my room?[%p]"

msgid "15200:床には僕が食べ終わった後のコンビニ弁当の容器とかが散乱しているし、ベッドの上には過激なイラストが描かれたエロゲの箱が積み上げられているって言うのに。[%p]"
msgstr "15200:There were discarded food containers from the convenience store on the floor, and stacks of H-game boxes with XXX-rated covers on the bed.[%p]"

msgid "15300:よっぽど梨深の神経が太いのか、僕が警戒されていないのか。どっちにしろ複雑な気分だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "15300:Either Rimi was really brave, or she didn't see me as any kind of potential threat at all. I wasn't sure how I felt about either option.[%p]"

msgid "15400:梨深は僕のそんな苦悩なんてまったく気付いていないらしく、ソファに座ってファンタズムのＣＤの歌詞カードを真剣に眺めている。[%p]"
msgstr "15400:Rimi didn't seem to have noticed my discomfort at all, though. She sat down on the sofa, and was staring at the lyrics booklet from the Phantasm CD.[%p]"

msgid "15500:僕はＰＣ用のイスにどっかりと腰を下ろした。身体の緊張をほどく。[%p]"
msgstr "15500:I sat down on my computer chair. At last, I could relax.[%p]"

msgid "15600:怯え続けていたからか今日は精神がすり減ったけど、それほど疲れを感じてないのは梨深が一緒にいてくれたからかな……。[%p]"
msgstr "15600:Fear had worn me down today, but I didn't feel as tired as I thought I would. Probably because Rimi was here with me.[%p]"

msgid "15700:[name]梨深[line]「さて、どうしよっか」[%p]"
msgstr "15700:[name]梨深[line]Now, what should we do?[%p]"

msgid "15800:歌詞カードを閉じた梨深が、大きく伸びをしてから僕に笑みを送ってきた。[%p]"
msgstr "15800:She shut the lyrics booklet and gave a big stretch as she smiled at me.[%p]"

msgid "15900:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "15900:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16000:どうしようって言われても……どうすればいいんだ？[%p]"
msgstr "16000:What should we do? Don't ask me.[%p]"

msgid "16100:そもそも梨深は遊びに来たわけじゃない。[linebreak]ＣＤを貸すっていうのも当初の目的じゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "16100:Rimi hadn't come here to hang out. She hadn't come to borrow a CD, either.[%p]"

msgid "16200:ここに一緒にいてくれるとして、いったいなにをすればいいんだろう？[%p]"
msgstr "16200:I was glad she was staying here, but what exactly were we supposed to do?[%p]"

msgid "16300:そもそもなにかをしなくちゃいけないのか？[%p]"
msgstr "16300:Did we have to do anything?[%p]"

msgid "16400:エロゲだったら即、Ｈシーンに突入するんだろうけど……。[%p]"
msgstr "16400:If this was an H-game, we'd go straight to an H-scene, but...[%p]"

msgid "16500:って、やばいやばい。[linebreak]今はそういうことを考えない方がいい。[%p]"
msgstr "16500:No, no. I shouldn't be thinking about stuff like that right now.[%p]"

msgid "16600:ただでさえ、三次元の女子と部屋にふたりきりっていう、僕にしてみれば緊迫のシチュエーションなんだ。[%p]"
msgstr "16600:Being alone in my room with a 3D girl was already a tense enough situation.[%p]"

msgid "16700:余計な妄想をしていたら意識しちゃって変なボロを出しちゃいかねない。[%p]"
msgstr "16700:If I started having delusions, I might end up saying something I regretted.[%p]"

msgid "16800:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16800:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "16900:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "16900:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "17000:沈黙。[%p]"
msgstr "17000:Silence.[%p]"

msgid "17100:梨深はぼんやりとして、床に散乱したマンガ本や、ベッドに積み上げられたエロゲを眺めている。[%p]"
msgstr "17100:Rimi was sitting there, staring at the manga on the floor and the H-games on the bed.[%p]"

msgid "17200:気まずい……。[%p]"
msgstr "17200:This was awkward.[%p]"

msgid "17300:なにか僕から喋った方がいいような気もするけど、話題と言えばゲームやアニメのことぐらいしか思い浮かばない。[%p]"
msgstr "17300:I felt like I should say something, but the only things I knew how to talk about were anime and video games.[%p]"

msgid "17400:梨深がそれらに詳しいとも思えないし。[%p]"
msgstr "17400:I couldn't imagine Rimi knew much about either of them.[%p]"

msgid "17500:そもそも一緒にいてくれるって言ったのは梨深なんだから、梨深からなにか話してくれないかな。[%p]"
msgstr "17500:It was Rimi who'd offered to stay with me. Maybe she'd say something.[%p]"

msgid "17600:僕に会話のリードを期待されても困る……。[%p]"
msgstr "17600:If she was hoping for me to take the lead in the conversation, she was asking the wrong person.[%p]"

msgid "17700:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "17700:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "17800:[name]梨深[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "17800:[name]梨深[line]...[%p]"

msgid "17900:やっぱり、三次元女子は苦手だ。[%p]"
msgstr "17900:I really hated dealing with 3D girls.[%p]"

msgid "18000:一緒にいてくれるのはありがたいけど、この沈黙のプレッシャーには耐えきれない……。[%p]"
msgstr "18000:I appreciated her being with me, but this silent pressure was unbearable.[%p]"

msgid "18100:この部屋が薄暗いっていうのも問題だよね。なんだか雰囲気が淫靡っぽいって錯覚しそうだ。[%p]"
msgstr "18100:Part of the problem was how dark this room was. It made the mood feel kind of... erotic.[%p]"

msgid "18200:いたたまれなくなって、僕はＰＣに向かった。[%p]"
msgstr "18200:I turned back to my PC, unable to bear the awkwardness anymore.[%p]"

msgid "18300:調べなくちゃいけないことがある。[%p]"
msgstr "18300:There was something I had to look up.[%p]"

msgid "18400:さっき学校で思いついたこと。ディソードを手に入れるためのヒントになるかもしれないこと。[%p]"
msgstr "18400:It was the idea I'd had back at the school. The one that might give me a hint towards finding the Di-Sword.[%p]"

msgid "18500:“頭に描いたものを、映像化することは可能なのか”[%p]"
msgstr "18500:“Is it possible to turn the thoughts in your head into a video?”[%p]"

msgid "18600:以前、セナから教えられたＶＲ技術や“人間は電気仕掛け”っていうあたりを取っ掛かりに、さらに突き詰めて調べていってみよう。[%p]"
msgstr "18600:What Sena had told me before about VR technology and how “humans run on electricity” felt like it could be a good starting point.[%p]"

msgid "18700:[name]梨深[line]「なにしてるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "18700:[name]梨深[line]What are you doing?[%p]"

msgid "18800:梨深が立ち上がって、僕の方に近寄ってきた。[%p]"
msgstr "18800:Rimi stood up and walked over to me.[%p]"

msgid "18900:えーっと、せ、説明した方がいいのかな。[%p]"
msgstr "18900:Hmm... S-Should I explain?[%p]"

msgid "19000:でもどう説明していいやら……めんどくさそう……。[%p]"
msgstr "19000:But how to explain? It felt like it would be a big pain in the ass.[%p]"

msgid "19100:[name]拓巳[line]「…………」[%p]"
msgstr "19100:[name]拓巳[line]...[%p]"

msgid "19200:[name]梨深[line]「ねえねえ。なにしてるか教えてよー」[%p]"
msgstr "19200:[name]梨深[line]Hey, hey. Tell me what you're doing![%p]"

msgid "19300:リアクションを返さないでいたら、梨深は僕の背中をつんつんと指でつついてきた。[%p]"
msgstr "19300:Since I didn't answer, Rimi started poking me in the back with her finger.[%p]"

msgid "19400:さ、さすがに無視するわけにもいかないか……。[%p]"
msgstr "19400:I-I couldn't just ignore her, right?[%p]"

msgid "19500:[name]拓巳[line]「き、君は……そのぅ、も、妄想が、げ、現実になるって、[linebreak]信じられる？」[%p]"
msgstr "19500:[name]拓巳[line]D-Do you believe that... Delusions can become real?[%p]"

msgid "19600:僕はブラウザに検索キーワードを入力しつつ、梨深の方は見ずに、むしろ星来たんに話しかけているつもりで口を動かした。[%p]"
msgstr "19600:I kept typing search keywords into the browser instead of looking back at her. If anything, I was looking at Seira-tan as I spoke.[%p]"

msgid "19700:[name]梨深[line]「妄想が現実に？」[%p]"
msgstr "19700:[name]梨深[line]Delusions becoming real?[%p]"

msgid "19800:[name]梨深[line]「あはは、無理でしょー」[%p]"
msgstr "19800:[name]梨深[line]Ahaha! No way.[%p]"

msgid "19900:[name]梨深[line]「もしそれができたら、人はとっくに万能になってるよ」[%p]"
msgstr "19900:[name]梨深[line]If that was possible, humans could do anything they wanted.[%p]"

msgid "20000:万能……か。確かにそうかもしれない。[%p]"
msgstr "20000:Anything they wanted, huh? That might be true.[%p]"

msgid "20100:妄想っていうのはどんな非現実的なことでも可能な世界。それが現実になるなら……非現実が現実と化すっていうことになる。[%p]"
msgstr "20100:In your delusions, you could do anything, no matter how unreal. If those delusions could become real... that would mean the unreal could become real, too.[%p]"

msgid "20200:[name]梨深[line]「それがどうしたの？」[%p]"
msgstr "20200:[name]梨深[line]Why?[%p]"

msgid "20300:[name]拓巳[line]「それに、ち、近いシステムが……ア、アメリカで、[linebreak]その、えっと……特許……あるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "20300:[name]拓巳[line]T-There's a patent... For a system that's kind of like that... in America.[%p]"

msgid "20400:[name]梨深[line]「え〜、冗談でしょ？」[%p]"
msgstr "20400:[name]梨深[line]Aw, you're kidding.[%p]"

msgid "20500:僕の背後で、梨深が呆れたようにため息をつく気配を感じる。[%p]"
msgstr "20500:I wasn't looking at her, but I could sense her giving me a sigh of disbelief.[%p]"

msgid "20600:そこで、ＳＨＩＨＯが拾ってきてくれた例の特許画像を表示してやる。[%p]"
msgstr "20600:I decided to show her the image of the patent that Shiho had found for me.[%p]"

msgid "20700:[name]梨深[line]「ん？\u3000これは？」[%p]"
msgstr "20700:[name]梨深[line]Hmm? What's this?[%p]"

msgid "20800:[name]拓巳[line]「と、特許の……証拠、しゃ、写真」[%p]"
msgstr "20800:[name]拓巳[line]A-A picture... of the patent.[%p]"

msgid "20900:[name]梨深[line]「え、ホントに？」[%p]"
msgstr "20900:[name]梨深[line]Huh? Really?[%p]"

msgid "21000:梨深が身を乗り出してきて、モニタに顔を近づける。[%p]"
msgstr "21000:She leaned forward and stared at the monitor.[%p]"

msgid "21100:僕の顔のすぐ横からのぞき込むような形になった。[%p]"
msgstr "21100:Her head was now right next to mine.[%p]"

msgid "21200:[name]梨深[line]「うわ、あたし英語って苦手……」[%p]"
msgstr "21200:[name]梨深[line]Uwah... my English is so bad.[%p]"

msgid "21300:[name]梨深[line]「すごいね、タク。英語読めるなんて」[%p]"
msgstr "21300:[name]梨深[line]Wow, Taku. I didn't realize you could read English.[%p]"

msgid "21400:ち、近い……。[%p]"
msgstr "21400:S-She was so close.[%p]"

msgid "21500:モニタの光に反射してキラキラ光る彼女の瞳の輝きまで確認できるぐらいの距離。また僕はドギマギしてしまう。[%p]"
msgstr "21500:I could even see the sparkle in her eyes as the monitor's light reflected off them. My heart skipped a beat again.[%p]"

msgid "21600:[name]梨深[line]「ねえねえ、どういうことか教えてよ」[%p]"
msgstr "21600:[name]梨深[line]Hey, tell me what it says![%p]"

msgid "21700:どうやら興味を持ったらしかった。[%p]"
msgstr "21700:She seemed to have taken an interest.[%p]"

msgid "21800:僕は梨深の近さはなるべく考えないようにして、とにかくモニタと星来たんだけを交互に視界に入れるよう心がける。[%p]"
msgstr "21800:I tried my best not to think about how close she was, moving my head so that I could see both Seira-tan and the monitor at all times.[%p]"

msgid "21900:[name]拓巳[line]「う、生まれながらに、盲目の、ひ、人でも、ビデオカメラみたいな[linebreak]……え、えっと、映像機器を、と、と、通すことで、そこに、う、[linebreak]映る、景色が見えるように、な、なるんだ。これ、豆知識……な」[%p]"
msgstr "21900:[name]拓巳[line]L-Let's say... somebody was blind from birth. Um... you could like... send images through a video camera... so that they could... see. Got that?[%p]"

msgid "22000:[name]梨深[line]「ビデオカメラが目の代わりっていうこと？」[%p]"
msgstr "22000:[name]梨深[line]You mean the video camera would act as their eyes?[%p]"

msgid "22100:[name]拓巳[line]「そ、そう。……ＶＲ、技術、って言うんだよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "22100:[name]拓巳[line]Y-Yeah... It's called VR technology.[%p]"

msgid "22200:[name]梨深[line]「へ〜。もしホントだったらすごいなあ」[%p]"
msgstr "22200:[name]梨深[line]Huh... If that's true, it's really amazing.[%p]"

msgid "22300:だからホントなんだってば。[%p]"
msgstr "22300:It is true.[%p]"

msgid "22400:テストだって成功したって、セナが言ってたし。[%p]"
msgstr "22400:Sena said that they'd even succeeded in testing it.[%p]"

msgid "22500:[name]梨深[line]「んー、でも……」[%p]"
msgstr "22500:[name]梨深[line]Hmm... but...[%p]"

msgid "22600:[name]梨深[line]「機械を使って目が見えるようになるのと、妄想が現実になるって、どう繋がるの？」[%p]"
msgstr "22600:[name]梨深[line]What's using a machine to see have to do with delusions being real?[%p]"

msgid "22700:[name]梨深[line]「あたし、頭悪いからよく分かんないや、たはは……」[%p]"
msgstr "22700:[name]梨深[line]I'm not that smart, so I can't figure it out. Tahaha...[%p]"

msgid "22800:梨深に説明をしつつも、引っかかりそうなキーワードで手当たり次第に検索してみるけど、なかなか思ったようなページを見つけられない。[%p]"
msgstr "22800:As I explained my theory to Rimi, I kept on typing keywords into the search engine. But nothing was coming up.[%p]"

msgid "22900:それでも根気強く、新しいキーワードを入力し続ける。[%p]"
msgstr "22900:I kept going anyway.[%p]"

msgid "23000:[name]拓巳[line]「映像機器に映る、け、景色も、脳内で思い浮かべた、も、妄想も……電気信号だから……」[%p]"
msgstr "23000:[name]拓巳[line]B-Both the images coming from the camera... and the delusions in your mind... are just... electrical signals.[%p]"

msgid "23100:[name]梨深[line]「う〜ん？」[%p]"
msgstr "23100:[name]梨深[line]Hmm?[%p]"

msgid "23200:[name]拓巳[line]「ぎゃ、逆に考えるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "23200:[name]拓巳[line]T-Think of it the other way around.[%p]"

msgid "23300:[name]拓巳[line]「脳内に電気信号を送るんじゃなくて、脳内から電気信号を送るって、考えるんだ……」[%p]"
msgstr "23300:[name]拓巳[line]Don't think about sending signals to the brain... think about sending signals from the brain.[%p]"

msgid "23400:[name]梨深[line]「ほほ〜」[%p]"
msgstr "23400:[name]梨深[line]I see.[%p]"

msgid "23500:返ってくるのは曖昧な返事ばっかり。[%p]"
msgstr "23500:Her responses were dull, almost blank.[%p]"

msgid "23600:あんまりよく分かってない……のかも……。[%p]"
msgstr "23600:Maybe she didn't understand at all.[%p]"

msgid "23700:詳しく説明するのも面倒だったから、僕はそれ以上語るのをやめた。調べ物に集中する。[%p]"
msgstr "23700:I was tired of explaining things to her, so I just stopped talking. I focused on my research.[%p]"

msgid "23800:まあ、別に分かってもらえなくてもいいさ。[linebreak]所詮、僕が思いついた推測でしかないんだから。[%p]"
msgstr "23800:I didn't really need her to understand, anyway. It was just an idea I'd come up with.[%p]"

msgid "23900:[name]梨深[line]「ふむふむ〜？」[%p]"
msgstr "23900:[name]梨深[line]Hmm, hmm...[%p]"

msgid "24000:梨深はいまだにひとりでうなったりコクコクうなずいたりしている。[%p]"
msgstr "24000:Rimi was still nodding and murmuring even though I'd stopped talking.[%p]"

msgid "24100:もうほっとこう。[%p]"
msgstr "24100:I decided to just ignore her.[%p]"

msgid "24200:いろいろ検索はかけているけど、なかなか僕の推測を実証してくれるような資料は見つからなかった。[%p]"
msgstr "24200:But no matter how much I searched, I couldn't find anything to back up my theory.[%p]"

msgid "24300:少しアプローチの仕方を変えて、今度は特許方面から重点的に検索をかけてみよう。[%p]"
msgstr "24300:I decided to change my approach and look at patents instead of just web pages.[%p]"

msgid "24400:ＳＨＩＨＯに教えてもらった、アメリカの特許についてまとめた海外サイトに行ってみる。[%p]"
msgstr "24400:I went to the English site that Shiho had told me about that had a list of patents.[%p]"

msgid "24500:そこで、それっぽい特許がないかどうか探す。[%p]"
