msgid "24600:[name]拓巳[line]「あ……！」[%p]"
msgstr "24600:[name]拓巳[line]Oh![%p]"

msgid "24700:いくつかリンクを辿っていくうちに、ようやく前にＳＨＩＨＯが拾ってくれたものと似た雰囲気の画像がヒットした。どうやらＶＲ装置とは違う特許書類の画像らしい。[%p]"
msgstr "24700:After following a bunch of links, I finally found something similar to what Shiho had shown me before. It was a different patent document than the one for the VR device.[%p]"

msgid "24800:さっそく内容を読んでみる。[%p]"
msgstr "24800:I decided to read it immediately.[%p]"

msgid "24900:[name]拓巳[line]「『神経信号パルスを遠隔地からモニターし、それを映像および音声として再現する装置と方法』……！」[%p]"
msgstr "24900:[name]拓巳[line]“A method and device for the remote monitoring of nerve impulses, and their replication in audio and video form”…![%p]"

msgid "25000:[name]梨深[line]「おお〜？」[%p]"
msgstr "25000:[name]梨深[line]Ooh?[%p]"

msgid "25100:まさに僕が考えた通りの内容じゃないか！[%p]"
msgstr "25100:It was just what I'd thought of![%p]"

msgid "25200:僕は思わずイスから腰を浮かしていた。[%p]"
msgstr "25200:I leaned forward out of my chair.[%p]"

msgid "25300:[name]拓巳[line]「こ、これ……す、すごいぞ……っ」[%p]"
msgstr "25300:[name]拓巳[line]T-This is... incredible![%p]"

msgid "25400:[name]梨深[line]「ん？\u3000すごいの？\u3000なにがなにが？」[%p]"
msgstr "25400:[name]梨深[line]Hmm? Incredible? What's incredible?[%p]"

msgid "25500:[name]拓巳[line]「か、簡単に……言うと……こ、これ……」[%p]"
msgstr "25500:[name]拓巳[line]It's basically a device...[%p]"

msgid "25600:[name]拓巳[line]「他人の“思考を盗撮する”……技術だ……」[%p]"
msgstr "25600:[name]拓巳[line]for reading people's thoughts.[%p]"

msgid "25700:[name]梨深[line]「思考を……盗撮……」[%p]"
msgstr "25700:[name]梨深[line]Reading thoughts...[%p]"

msgid "25800:つまり、人間が頭の中で考えている音や映像を、特殊な機器を使って盗み見ることができるっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "25800:In other words, you could use a special device to take a look at the images and sounds inside a person's head.[%p]"

msgid "25900:しかも神経信号パルスのモニタリングは、人工衛星を使って行うことさえ可能って書いてある……。[linebreak]これなら、対象者が地球上のどこにいても盗撮は可能だ……。[%p]"
msgstr "25900:And it even said you could monitor these nerve impulses from satellites. With this, you could read the mind of anybody on Earth.[%p]"

msgid "26000:[name]梨深[line]「ホントにそんなことできるの？\u3000ＳＦ小説とか、そういう類のものなんじゃ……？」[%p]"
msgstr "26000:[name]梨深[line]Is that really possible? It's not from a sci-fi novel or something?[%p]"

msgid "26100:[name]拓巳[line]「と、特許って……そのシステム自体が、か、完全に仕上がって、ないと……」[%p]"
msgstr "26100:[name]拓巳[line]P-Patents require you... to have the finished system...[%p]"

msgid "26200:[name]拓巳[line]「ぜ、ぜ、絶対に、取得できないんだって……」[%p]"
msgstr "26200:[name]拓巳[line]b-b-before you can get them.[%p]"

msgid "26300:ネットで特許のことについて調べたら、そう書いてあった。[%p]"
msgstr "26300:That's what I'd read when I'd looked up patents online.[%p]"

msgid "26400:[name]拓巳[line]「だ、だか、ら……これも……ちゃ、ちゃんとシステムが、確立されてるって……ことだよ……」[%p]"
msgstr "26400:[name]拓巳[line]S-So this system... has to be real.[%p]"

msgid "26500:これはフィクションじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "26500:This wasn't fiction.[%p]"

msgid "26600:システムを構築する技術力と金さえあれば、いつでも実現可能だっていうこと。[%p]"
msgstr "26600:If you had the money and technological prowess to make the system, you could do it any time you wanted.[%p]"

msgid "26700:セナは、こう言っていた。[%p]"
msgstr "26700:I remembered what Sena had said.[%p]"

msgid "26800:[name]セナ[line]「ある意図的な情報を、[linebreak]神経パルスへコンバートすることが可能なら――」[%p]"
msgstr "26800:[name]セナ[line]If it were possible to convert a certain deliberately-chosen information pattern into nerve impulses...[%p]"

msgid "26900:[name]セナ[line]「人の五感すべて、さらには人の意志そのものもコントロールできるんじゃないか？」[%p]"
msgstr "26900:[name]セナ[line]You would be able to control all five of a person's senses, and in fact, their will itself.[%p]"

msgid "27000:その説についてはソースが出てこなかったから、あくまでセナの推測でしかない。[%p]"
msgstr "27000:I hadn't found any source to confirm or deny that. So, it was just a guess.[%p]"

msgid "27100:でも、僕が思いついた説は……ソースがあった。[%p]"
msgstr "27100:But the theory I'd come up with... had a source.[%p]"

msgid "27200:なんで、こんな凄いニュースが日本ではまったく知られていないんだろう。[%p]"
msgstr "27200:Why wasn't this incredible news anywhere to be found in Japan?[%p]"

msgid "27300:はっきり言ってノーベル賞ものだと思うんだけど。[%p]"
msgstr "27300:It felt like you could win a Nobel for it easily.[%p]"

msgid "27400:僕は続けて、思考盗撮というキーワードで検索をかけてみた。[%p]"
msgstr "27400:I decided to search for things involving mind reading.[%p]"

msgid "27500:すると、アメリカのとある訴訟記録が出てきた。[%p]"
msgstr "27500:What I found was a record of an American court proceeding.[%p]"

msgid "27600:[name]梨深[line]「うわ、また英文だ……」[%p]"
msgstr "27600:[name]梨深[line]Ugh, English again.[%p]"

msgid "27700:[name]梨深[line]「頭痛くなってきそうだよー」[%p]"
msgstr "27700:[name]梨深[line]My head's starting to hurt.[%p]"

msgid "27800:けっこう長文だから、僕も読むのが面倒くさかった。[%p]"
msgstr "27800:It was pretty long, so I didn't feel like trying to read it all.[%p]"

msgid "27900:ちょっと変な文章になるかもしれないけど、翻訳ソフトを使って和訳してみる。[%p]"
msgstr "27900:I decided to use translation software on it, even if it meant I might end up with something a little off.[%p]"

msgid "28000:書かれている内容は、まとめるとこんな感じ。[%p]"
msgstr "28000:The basic idea was something like this:[%p]"

msgid "28100:訴訟記録[linebreak]原告、Ｎ・Ｋ・ラビン[linebreak]被告、アメリカ合衆国国防総省、中央情報局[%p]"
msgstr "28100:Legal Proceedings: Plaintiff: N.K. Rabin Defendant: United States Department of Defense, Central Intelligence Agency[%p]"

msgid "28200:●原告による主張[%p]"
msgstr "28200:● Plaintiff's Claims[%p]"

msgid "28300:私の思考は、特殊な機器によって盗み見られ、記録され、衛星を使っていずこかへと転送されている。[%p]"
msgstr "28300:My thoughts are being scanned by a special device, recorded, and sent somewhere via satellite.[%p]"

msgid "28400:私は衛星による人質だ。昼夜絶え間なく、いくつもの衛星によって攻撃にもさらされた。[%p]"
msgstr "28400:I am a hostage to the satellites. I am exposed to attack by multiple satellites, night and day.[%p]"

msgid "28500:①追跡\u3000②思考監視[linebreak]③全身の監視\u3000④バイオ周波数攻撃[linebreak]⑤音声攻撃\u3000⑥肉体の衰弱化[%p]"
msgstr "28500:1. Tracking 2. Mind-Reading[linebreak]3. Observation of My Entire Body 4. Bio-Frequency Attacks[linebreak]5. Audio Attacks 6. Inducement of Physical Weakness[%p]"

msgid "28600:１９９０年１２月下旬以来、私は睡眠中に、人為的に作られた夢（映像的、および音声的内容を持ち、声の内容も含む）を見せられた。[%p]"
msgstr "28600:Beginning in late December 1990, I have been shown artificially-created dreams (including audio, visual, and voice content) during my sleep.[%p]"

msgid "28700:１９９２年２月〜５月にかけて、私はバイオ周波数攻撃（苦痛、拷問、ハラスメント）を受けた。[%p]"
msgstr "28700:Between the months of February and May, 1992, I was a victim of bio-frequency attacks (pain, torture, harassment.)[%p]"

msgid "28800:これらが私に対する攻撃だと認識し、１９９２年２月から、私はノートに以下の記録を記した。[linebreak]・日付\u3000・時間\u3000・特に顕著で苦痛を覚えた精神攻撃の内容[%p]"
msgstr "28800:I recognized that these were attacks upon my person, and beginning in February 1992, I began to record the following in my notes. ・Time ・Date ・Contents of particularly painful psychological attacks[%p]"

msgid "28900:バイオ周波数攻撃は私の身体のあらゆる部分に対して行われた。苦痛、拷問、ハラスメントは私の身体の一部、時には全身に、不快感、疲労、苦痛を与えるべく調整されていた。[%p]"
msgstr "28900:These bio-frequency attacks were performed upon every part of my body. The pain, torture, and harassment were finely tuned so that they would cause unpleasurable sensations, exhaustion, and pain to parts, and sometimes all, of my body.[%p]"

msgid "29000:主な部位は以下の通りである。[%p]"
msgstr "29000:The major parts of my body that were affected are as follows.[%p]"

msgid "29100:・胸部\u3000・視覚\u3000・下腹部[linebreak]・脳（睡眠障害を引き起こすための）[linebreak]・脳（人工的な夢を見させるための）[%p]"
msgstr "29100:・Chest ・Vision ・Abdomen ・Brain (to cause sleep disorders)[linebreak]・Brain (to cause me to have artificial dreams.)[%p]"

msgid "29200:[name]拓巳[line]「思考監視、思考盗撮……しかも国家ぐるみ……」[%p]"
msgstr "29200:[name]拓巳[line]Mind-reading, stealing thoughts... and the government's behind it.[%p]"

msgid "29300:[name]拓巳[line]「……ちょ、マジ？」[%p]"
msgstr "29300:[name]拓巳[line]Is this serious?[%p]"

msgid "29400:[name]梨深[line]「あー、あたしこれ知ってる。何年か前に映画で見た！」[%p]"
msgstr "29400:[name]梨深[line]Oh, I know this! I saw it in a movie a few years back![%p]"

msgid "29500:それはフィクションでしょ……。[%p]"
msgstr "29500:That was just fiction, wasn't it?[%p]"

msgid "29600:でも、ここに書かれている訴訟記録はそうじゃない。[%p]"
msgstr "29600:But these court proceedings were real.[%p]"

